{"abstract":[{"text":"The Cocoa frameworks give you high-level access to the underlying power of Mac OS X. Get a developer’s eye overview of the Lion advances in Foundation and Application Kit, including support for new features such as Full-screen, Auto Save, Resume, Versions, and many others. This session will orient you for the other Cocoa sessions that cover these technologies in further detail.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"role":"sampleCode","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"roleHeading":"WWDC11","title":"What’s New in Cocoa"},"kind":"article","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc11-101-whats-new-in-cocoa"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex","type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/101\/","isActive":true},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11-101-Whats-New-in-Cocoa"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC11"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"references":{"https://nonstrict.eu/wwdcindex/wwdc2011/101/":{"type":"download","identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/101\/","checksum":null,"url":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2011\/101\/"},"WWDC11-Icon.png":{"identifier":"WW